  "body": "###  What have you changed?\r\n\r\nThis PR wakes up leader for more cases:\r\n- Singleton can become leader in a tick, which breaks the hibernate check.\r\n    This patch verifies if it's still follower to prevent it from hibernating.\r\n- If leader sleeps during pre-transfer leader phase, it will keep sleep until other follower campaigns.\r\n- If a learner disconnect for a while, it can't be prompted until next check invalid timeout.\r\n\r\n\r\nClose #6668 \r\n\r\n###  What is the type of the changes?\r\n- Bugfix\r\n\r\n###  How is the PR tested?\r\n- Integration test\r\n\r\n###  Does this PR affect documentation (docs) or should it be mentioned in the release notes?\r\nNo.\r\n\r\n###  Does this PR affect `tidb-ansible`?\r\nNo.\r\n\r\n###  Refer to a related PR or issue link (optional)\r\n#6668 \r\n\r\n\r\n",
